// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/M3lBRS sphere sphere intersection, 2024 by jt
// using https://www.shadertoy.com/view/MffcWr oriented ring

// Implementation of https://mathworld.wolfram.com/Sphere-SphereIntersection.html
// rewritten with help of https://www.wolframalpha.com to reduce number of sqrt.

// tags: sphere, intersection, geometry, ray, marching

